OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPlenty of sunshine through the
OL,6,Fday, once any morning shallow mist or
OL,7,Ffog patches clear. Some fair weather
OL,8,Fcloud may bubble up through the day
OL,9,Fwithin the light winds. Feeling warmer
OL,10,Ffor many especially in the sun.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FTurning cloudier from the
OL,13,Fwest overnight which can produce some
OL,14,Fspots of rain at times. Winds stay
OL,15,Flight but a mild night for many.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA cloudy start to the
OL,18,Fweekend but lifting and breaking
OL,19,Fthrough the morning to leave plenty of
OL,20,Fbright and sunny spells, mostly in the
OL,21,Fsouth. Light winds and feeling warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
